      Mexico How to Contact the Mexican Consumer Protection Authorities

   The following information will allow you to contact the Mexican
   consumer protection authorities directly:

   Internet Website:

     www.profeco.gob.mx (Spanish; complaint forms in Spanish, English,
     and French)

   Telephonic Inquiries:

     (52 5) 5 68 87 22

     01 800 90 31 300 (toll free inside Mexico)

   Fax Inquiries:

     (52 5) 2 11 15 37

   E-Mail Inquiries:

     Quejas@profeco.gob.mx

     dproyes@profeco.gob.mx


